---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Pregunta" description="Learn more about Pregunta">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8">About Pregunta</h1>
    <div class="prose dark:prose-invert mx-auto">
      <p>Pregunta is a modern and interactive quiz game designed to be both fun and educational.</p>
      <h2>Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Modern and responsive interface</li>
        <li>Light/dark mode</li>
        <li>Multiple language support</li>
        <li>Solo and multiplayer game modes</li>
        <li>Score system and achievements</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
